-- OSX Said to Be Filing for Bankruptcy Protection in Rio Today
-- B y   C r i s t i a n e   L u c c h e s i
-- 2013-11-11T18:48:51Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-11-11/osx-said-to-be-filing-for-bankruptcy-protection-in-rio-today.html
Eike Batista ’s shipbuilder OSX
Brasil SA is filing for  bankruptcy protection  today, according
to a person with direct knowledge of the case.  OSX lawyers will submit documents in a Rio de Janeiro
court, said the person, asking not to be named before the
request has been made public.  The shipbuilder’s board approved the so-called judicial
recovery petition, switched advisers and will seek to change its
name, address and board composition, the Rio-based company said
in a Nov. 8 statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
